  <introduction lang="en">
    This component checks a random number generator on its randomness according to the <i>Dieharder</i> tests.
  </introduction>

  <introduction lang="de-DE">
    Diese Komponente testet den Output eines Zufallszahlengenerator auf seine Zufälligkeit mittels der <i>Dieharder</i>-Testbatterie.
  </introduction>

  <usage lang="en">
    <list>
      <item>Put a random number generator on the workspace and connect its output with the input of this component.</item>
      <item>Choose one of the tests of randomness listed in the settings of this component.</item>
      <item>Connect the output of this component with a TextOutput component.</item>
      <item>Start the workspace and you will get information about whether or not the generator was random according to the selected test.</item>
    </list>
    
